Debian package for Sun's Java JDK: java-package
  apt install java-package
  fakeroot make-jpkg jre-1_5_0_06-linux-i586.bin
  dpkg -i sun-j2re1.5_1.5.0+update06_i386.deb
More info here:
http://wiki.serios.net/wiki/Debian_Java_JRE/JDK_installation_with_java-package

